<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦١٨٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4972">عَيَّاشُ بْنُ الْوَلِيدِ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3160">عَبْدُ الْأَعْلَى: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6279">مَعْمَرٌ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">الزُّهْرِيِّ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3745">أَبِي سَلَمَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a>عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«لَا تُسَمُّوا الْعِنَبَ الْكَرْمَ، وَلَا تَقُولُوا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>خَيْبَةَ الدَّهْرِ؛ فَإِنَّ اللهَ هُوَ الدَّهْرُ.»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>